data.description: Welcoming, covered front porch as you enter into the living room with plenty of natural light, galley kitchen with lots of cabinetry and eating area highlighted by double windows to view back yard as you are eating, also access to full basement. There are three carpeted bedrooms, updated full bath with step-in shower & tile flooring, attached double garage with a 19 x 12 tool room addition on back. Just add your special touches to make this house a home!
